SUMMARY:WHISKEY WEDNESDAY at ALLEY TWENTY SIX
DESCRIPTION:Whiskey lovers\, mark your calendars: Whiskey Wednesday at Alley Twenty Six is your chance to explore premium pours at unbeatable prices. Every Wednesday\, the team selects a standout bottle to offer at break-even cost—often in collaboration with Bull City Bourbon Club. On the third Wednesday of the month\, guest expert Che Ramos (aka The Black Bourbon Guy) curates the selection and will be on hand to share tasting notes. This month’s lineup includes: \nNov. 5: Smooth Ambler Old Scout Single Barrel Rye\, $4\nNov. 12: Elijah Craig Single Barrel Bourbon “I’m Hot Sticky Sweet\,” $5\nNov. 19: Aberlour 16 Year Single Malt Scotch\, $9\nNov. 26: Woodford Reserve Double Oaked Single Barrel Bourbon\, $5 \nAlley Twenty Six is located at 320 E. Chapel Hill St.\, Durham. Info: alleytwentysix.com
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/whiskey-wednesday-at-alley-twenty-six-5/2026-03-11/
LOCATION:Alley Twenty Six\, 320 E Chapel Hill St\, Durham\, NC\, 27701\, United States
CATEGORIES:Food & Drink,Special Offer,Wines, Spirits, Beer and Cheer
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://downtowndurham.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/rsz_whiskey_wednesday_bourbon_image1.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Alley Twenty Six":MAILTO:noreply@facebookmail.com
GEO:35.9967606;-78.9004853
