SUMMARY:Bull McCabes Weekly Trivia
DESCRIPTION:Join us every Wednesday at 8pm for Trivia hosted by our beloved King of Trivia: Arturo Sanchez! You can play from anywhere on our grounds: grab a seat at the bar\, a booth inside\, or a table on the covered patio or the lawn\, and submit answers from your phone! There are three rounds\, with the second round always having a dedicated theme that we post on our Instagram account (@bullmccabesdnc) and from the trivia account (@bullmccabes_trivia)\, so make sure to follow both accounts! Winners receive $50 off their bar tab\, 2nd place gets $25 off\, and there are two shout out rounds with swag and prizes to win from our sponsors (like Vaguely Reminiscent & the Carolina Theatre!)\, plus there are prizes for the best team name\, and even a prize for last place! Come find out what the best Trivia in town is about with challenging fresh questions\, and the sassiest host there is!
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/bull-mccabes-weekly-trivia/2026-03-11/
LOCATION:Bull McCabes\, 427 W Main St\, Durham\, NC\, 27701\, United States
CATEGORIES:Trivia
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://downtowndurham.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Screenshot-2025-06-05-at-11.11.30 PM.jpeg
ORGANIZER;CN="Casey Oster":MAILTO:bullmccabesdnc@gmail.com
GEO:35.9972527;-78.9050206
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Bull McCabes 427 W Main St Durham NC 27701 United States;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=427 W Main St:geo:-78.9050206,35.9972527
END:VEVENT
