SUMMARY:Encaustic Painting
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an immersive and hands-on encaustic painting workshop for only $25! We believe art should feel accessible\, hands-on\, and a little transformative. Whether you’ve never touched encaustic before or you’re ready to push your practice further\, our workshops are designed to grow your skills\, build your confidence\, and plug you into a creative community that supports you.\nCome fuse your ideas.\nFracture the rules.\nCreate something that belongs to you — and to Durham.
