SUMMARY:Silent Book Club Thursdays @ DSSOLVR (FREE)
DESCRIPTION:Silent Book Club – Durham \nJoin us for an evening of literary camaraderie at DSSOLVR’s Durham taproom! Weekly on Thursdays\, starting @ 6:30 pm\, the @SilentBookClub convenes to celebrate the joy of reading with fellow book lovers. \nCome read and mingle with new\, bookish friends! Bring whatever book you happen to be reading\, read in companionable silence (for about an hour)\, then share about it with your table mates. \nSchedule: \n– Meet and chat until 6:30 – 7:00 \n– Silent reading 7:00 – 8:00 \n– Chat about reading 8:00 – ??? \nWi-Fi – Free guest Wi-Fi available.\nDogs – Dog Friendly inside & outside.\nFamily – Family friendly w/ high chair\, changing table\, and sensory toys for kids. Free to play video Games & board games available.\nFood – Snacks available on site. Several food delivery & carry out options available within a 2 block radius.\nParking – Street parking available all around as well as free parking lot a block away next to Welcome Tattoo and two blocks away behind Cocoa Cinnamon.\nMenu – Menu has rotating options of beer\, cider\, Gluten free beers\, liquor/cocktails\, Jell-O shots\, and extensive non-alcoholic offerings!
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/silent-book-club-sundays-dssolvr-free-2/2026-03-12/
