DESCRIPTION:Join your Durham neighbors every Thursday night for Music Trivia Bingo with the one and only Stormie Daie! Grab a table with your crew and play any or all of 3 fun rounds curated by Stormie and sampled by her special guest DJs Gay Agenda or Jorden The DJ\, who alternate weekly! Each round’s winner gets a prize\, and it’s always free to participate. A great way to spend a weeknight with friends – and meet some new ones! Drink specials\, no cover\, 21+ with valid ID to enter.
